<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Fitness Club</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

  <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">

  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f3fff4;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #28a745;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .content-box {
      background-color: white;
      border: 2px solid #28a745;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    blockquote {
      border-left: 5px solid #28a745;
      padding-left: 15px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555;
    }

    hr {
      border-color: #28a745;
    }

    dt {
      color: #28a745;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Display Headings -->
  <p class="display-1 text-center">FITNESS CLUB</p>
  <p class="display-2 text-center">Stay Healthy</p>
  <p class="display-3 text-center">Exercise Every Day</p>
  <p class="display-4 text-center">Fitness Guide <small>for Beginners</small></p>

  <hr>

  <div class="content-box">

    <!-- Heading Classes -->
    <h2>Bootstrap Heading Classes</h2>

    <p class="h1">Warm-Up Session</p>
    <p class="h2">Cardio Exercise</p>
    <p class="h3">Strength Training</p>
    <p class="h4">Yoga Practice</p>
    <p class="h5">Healthy Diet</p>
    <p class="h6">Cool Down</p>

  </div>

  <div class="content-box">

    <!-- Lead, Mark, Small -->
    <h2>Healthy Living</h2>

    <p class="lead">
      Daily exercise helps us stay active, fit, and energetic.
    </p>

    <p>
      Drink <mark>plenty of water</mark> before and after your workout.
    </p>

    <p>
      <small>Always exercise safely and follow your trainer's instructions.</small>
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="content-box">

    <!-- Code and Abbreviation -->
    <h2>Useful Terms</h2>

    <p>The <code>push-up</code> is a simple bodyweight exercise.</p>

    <p>
      <abbr title="Body Mass Index">BMI</abbr> is commonly used to measure body weight in relation to height.
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="content-box">

    <!-- Blockquote -->
    <h2>Motivational Quote</h2>

    <blockquote>
      <p>"Take care of your body. It's the only place you have to live."</p>
      <footer>— Jim Rohn</footer>
    </blockquote>

  </div>

  <div class="content-box">

    <!-- Description List -->
    <h2>Workout Plan</h2>

    <dl>
      <dt>Running</dt>
      <dd>Improves heart health and stamina.</dd>

      <dt>Yoga</dt>
      <dd>Increases flexibility and reduces stress.</dd>

      <dt>Cycling</dt>
      <dd>Strengthens leg muscles and improves balance.</dd>

      <dt>Stretching</dt>
      <dd>Helps prevent muscle injuries before exercise.</dd>
    </dl>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
